			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hello,
<br />

<br />
there is no limit for the number of questions. The only important thing is to follow the PHP syntax. Try the following:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
$questions = array&#40;
<br />
'Are you human?' =&gt; array &#40;'yes', 'ja', 'oui'&#41;,
<br />
'Say &quot;AppleFun&quot;' =&gt; array &#40;'AppleFun', 'AppleFun', 'AppleFun'&#41;,
<br />
'Say &quot;George Bush&quot;' =&gt; array &#40;'George Bush', 'George Bush', 'George Bush'&#41;
<br />
&#41;;
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
